@node Main "Lightnix - Documentation"

                             'Lightnix' 1.0
                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Lightnix' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played on an 8 by 8 tiles
board, where you click on tiles of various patterns, this
will send 'lightning bolts' in 4 directions, vertically and
horizontally. If the lightning bolts hit identical tiles,
those tiles will be eliminated and you will get points
according to the number of removed tiles.

  Have fun!

